    "description": "Discipline: Qinggong\nSkill: Speed TN 7\nType: Counter\nQi: 4\n\nThis Technique can be used as a Counter whenever someone makes a Melee Attack against you. You pivot to avoid their attack, leading them to falter for just a moment so you finish the pivot, placing yourself behind them. On a Success you avoid their Attack and may respond using a mundane Attack that does 1 Extra Wound (due to surprise). Cathartic: You avoid the Attack and may counter with a mundane Attack or Kung Fu Technique, with surprise inflicting 1 Extra Wound.",
